                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I was called into the shop, and took the prisoner—I received these boots from Miss Fair—I found nothing but two duplicates on the prisoner—she had no money—another person was taken into custody, who had 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> The young woman with me was going to pay 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on the booti till we came home from work—I was selling things in a basket.</p>
